08:07.800 --> 08:10.800
The sun is hot.

08:10.800 --> 08:15.400
Hannah sits down on one of the park benches.

08:15.400 --> 08:18.920
The sun is in her eyes.

08:18.920 --> 08:22.360
So she closes them.

08:22.360 --> 08:25.520
When she opens her eyes again, she

08:25.520 --> 08:29.520
