13:19.160 --> 13:23.800
She calls, try again.

13:23.800 --> 13:33.840
So Hannah tries once more and falls off her skateboard again.

13:33.840 --> 13:40.680
She laughs, gets up and goes home.

13:40.680 --> 13:46.240
