14:22.440 --> 14:26.520
I can do good skateboard jumps now.

14:26.520 --> 14:28.520
Usually.

14:28.520 --> 14:33.360
That's wonderful, honey.

14:33.360 --> 14:36.720
Just then, Evan comes in.

14:36.800 --> 14:38.800
Oh, no.

14:38.800 --> 14:40.720
