15:30.560 --> 15:34.440
Oh, it's not bad.

15:34.440 --> 15:36.600
Hannah answers.

15:36.600 --> 15:39.640
And the helmet's awesome, too.

15:39.640 --> 15:44.720
But I have a lot of bruises now, look.

15:44.720 --> 15:49.800
Evan looks at the bruises all over her arms and legs.

15:49.800 --> 15:51.160
