15:52.840 --> 15:57.080
So, do you skateboard at the skate park now?

15:57.080 --> 15:58.640
No.

15:58.640 --> 16:00.560
Hannah answers.

16:00.560 --> 16:04.640
There are always a lot of people there.

16:04.640 --> 16:07.800
But I want to go up the walls.

16:07.800 --> 16:11.760
I want to turn in the air, too.

16:11.760 --> 16:18.400
Well, I go past the skate park every day when I go to work.

16:18.400 --> 16:21.840
