16:21.840 --> 16:27.640
Evan says, Evan, that's an awesome idea.

16:27.640 --> 16:29.480
Hannah cries.

16:29.480 --> 16:35.880
I can go there before school, thanks.

16:35.880 --> 16:40.800
Next day, Hannah gets up at six o'clock.

16:40.800 --> 16:46.160
